PAUL L stalked pace along the inside on the backstretch, continued along the rail on the turn, entered lane in the two path and finished up evenly. B D R DRAGSTER away cleanly, dropped to the back and trailed throughout, showed mild late progress in the lane. BETITO chased leader along the rail on the backstretch, continued to save ground on the turn, entered lane with some promise and failed to deliver when flattening out. WE MISS GENO tracked leader four wide on the backstretch, kept wide on the turn, drifted out and went into the lane in the seven path, and came up empty when asked.
